rd-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2>如何观看<em>《旋风斩</em>》？</h2><p> <em>《旋风</em>》共 12 集，将于 6 月 28 日在 Netflix 全球独家首播。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="zxx" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://t.co/yCLS8eZcUn">pic.twitter.com/yCLS8eZcUn</a></p><p> — Netflix K-Content (@netflixkcontent) <a href="https://twitter.com/netflixkcontent/status/1795968423995834748?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 30 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-k-drama-the-whirlwind-sul-kyung-gu-kim-hee-ae-cast-plot-trailer-3760727">景九和金喜爱在 Netflix 韩剧《旋风》的惊心动魄的预告片中对峙，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
